# BIOS bootloader bits that must PERSIST in the chroot so the
# config/hooks/500-crucible-bootfix.binary hook can copy isolinux.bin and
# ldlinux.c32 into binary/isolinux before ISO mastering. (The old live-build
# fork's own Check_package would install-then-REMOVE syslinux packages within
# the binary_syslinux stage; packages listed here are detected as already
# present and left alone — verified in the fork's functions/packages.sh.)
# Cost in the installed system: <1MB. Both are in noble universe.
isolinux
syslinux-common
